<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.alihaydarsucu.GitHubPuller</id>
  <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <name>GitHub Puller</name>
  <summary>Batch pull GitHub repositories</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GitHub Puller is a desktop application for cloning and updating multiple GitHub repositories.
      It is built with GTK4 and libadwaita.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>GTK4 + libadwaita interface</li>
      <li>Repository search and filtering</li>
      <li>Branch selection per repository</li>
      <li>Private repository support (with GitHub token)</li>
      <li>Clone or pull depending on repository state</li>
      <li>Parallel processing for selected repositories</li>
      <li>Saved target directory</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
